<D>__{don't let me die out here }
<A>__{she looks at him with fierce eyes full of determination. the look calms him, at least a little. she keys the ignition, lowers the passenger side window. the duct tape rips away as the window glides down, admitting a mini avalanche of powdery snow and a frigid blast of cold. she climbs out.}
